If a color is used at 100 times in a project once we decide to change color we need to chnage ot at 100 Times

Solution

1. CSS Variables

Syntax
:root{
--bgColor:white
}

--bgColor is acts as a variable

To use That Variable
E.g
background: var(--bgColor)

Overriding for particlaur Scenario/Case
E.g:
:root{
--bgColor:white
}
h1{
--bgColor:grey;
background: var(--bgColor)
}
